desc_long								关于这款游戏							Lightblade VR is a virtual reality training simulation for self-illumintated plasma blades. This is a childhood dream come true! Get trained by your personal robot and deflect all incoming laser beams!Top features:• Fight with one or two blades• Master four different training modes and extra challenges• Unlock five blade colors• Unlock four hilt variations• Stunning 3D visuals• Immersive fighting sounds• Beautiful minimalistic user interface• The latest series of training robotThis is a fan-made game without any in-app purchases or advertising.DISCLAIMERLightblade VR is not affiliated with, authorized or endorsed by, or in any way officially connected with, Hasbro, Inc., Lucasfilm Ltd., The Walt Disney Company, Disney Enterprises, Inc., or any of their affiliates.						
